+# Why You Cannot Fix `libxml2` Vulnerabilities via Code Patching in Containers
+
+This document explains why **CVE-2025-12863** in `libxml2` is a **false positive** (officially rejected CVE) in containerized environments, and why manual code patching is not a practical or safe solution.
+
+---
+
